in in this contest.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a restart\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"this contest\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hildebrandt with a front headlock.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hildebrandt\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"a front headlock\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this instance, the American unleashed a beautiful shuck which resulted in a takedown and a 3-2 lead.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999103833260362, \"rank\": 8.826410703378969e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this instance\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"a beautiful shuck\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"a takedown\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later in the period, that position came up again and Hildebrandt tried another shuck.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the period\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"that position\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"Hildebrandt\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"another shuck\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, Feng was ready and held strong before getting to Hildebrandt's legs for a takedown.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Feng\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"Hildebrandt's legs\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"a takedown\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1688}]}, 